texts.text: It is too early to fall so hard.
If you wish to prove your way is righteous,
Uh-oh, guys! Thor is running out of steam!
We said we'd stay out of it...
But between Gozu-Tennoh's upgrade and the Mantra Army,
If this fight continues, it'll affect the other world.
We're in real trouble, Jeng Yun.
It's impolite to interrupt a duel,
but we must protect our world.
Gozu-Tennoh! From here on out, you will face us.
You still wish to fight me? What curious creatures.
However, you should not underestimate the Mantra Army.
None among them will lose to demons serving human children.
We won't know until we try!
Hehe! Time to show these cocky punks what's up.
>you fail to get a single hit on Gozu-Tennoh.
I admire your relentless will despite no hope of victory.
>Everyone is struck by a fierce shock wave.
[sys user_name], I'll run out and distract Gozu-Tennoh.
Out of respect for such honesty, I will make this quick.
>Just as the next wave is released, you leap out!
We did it! Gozu-Tennoh is breaking apart again!
Now, now... You believed you could land a single blow on me?
yet you remain hopeless against a true warrior like me.
The path you walk has come to a dead end.
My iron fist is the only way...
>The broken pieces come together with a heavy thunk.
(He is all-powerful now. No one can defeat him.)
(My lonely road failed to take me higher after all...)
Gozu-Tennoh, you insist your path is the only answer.
There is more than one path.
Yes, you might get lost on an unmarked road.
But that's what it means to walk.
The key is to never stop. To bravely move forward.
It may look like a dead end,
but another path may open as long as you never give up.
You short-lived humans cannot but cling to fantasy.
Whenever I fight alongside my fellow Liberators,
I can feel our combined strength conquer despair.
I believe it will save our world!
I have my own way to go where I want to go.
Then allow me to snuff that light and show you real power.
It is time to face the truth!
>The air around Gozu-Tennoh tenses with massive energy.
So, the real battle starts now!
Newbie, Jeng Yun! We gotta scram!
Even so, I can't run away!
(Believe in your own path, and move ever forward...)
(Real strength is not found in strict discipline and control.)
(To me, true strength... A true warrior...)
(Even alone, he conquers every obstacle against all odds.)
(Some seek a united front, but I walk in solitude.)
>Thor stands up and returns Gozu-Tennoh's attack.
I will repay my debt to you here.
Burn into your memory the mighty power of Thor!
